author: ekoneil
msg: Switch the NetUI test webapp over to the Command pattern from the RequestInterceptor pattern.  This takes the XmlHttpRequestServlet request interceptors out of the list of global interceptors run for every request, forward, etc.
They will work in either place (until RequestInterceptor support is removed in the next point release).
